title: Navigate forwards into a radio group where no radio buttons are checked
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate forwards from here' link, navigate forwards into the 'Rating' radio group.
assertions: roleGroup nameGroupRating roleRadio nameOneStar stateRadioUnchecked positionRadio1 numberRadioButtonsGroup5 0:interactionModeEnabled

title: Navigate backwards into a radio group where no radio buttons are checked
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate backwards from here' link, navigate backwards into the 'Rating' radio group.",
assertions: roleGroup nameGroupRating roleRadio nameFiveStars 0:nameOneStar 0:positionRadio1 stateRadioUnchecked positionRadio5 numberRadioButtonsGroup5 0:interactionModeEnabled

title: Navigate forwards into a radio group where the first radio button is checked
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate forwards from here' link, navigate forwards into the 'Rating' radio group.
assertions: roleGroup nameGroupRating roleRadio nameOneStar stateRadioChecked positionRadio1 numberRadioButtonsGroup5 0:interactionModeEnabled

title: Navigate backwards into a radio group where the last radio button is checked
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate backwards from here' link, navigate backwards into the 'Rating' radio group.
assertions: roleGroup nameGroupRating roleRadio nameFiveStars stateRadioChecked positionRadio5 numberRadioButtonsGroup5 0:interactionModeEnabled

title: Navigate out of the start of a radio group
instructions: Starting at the 'five stars' radio button, navigate to the 'Navigate forwards from here' link.

title: Navigate out of the end of a radio group
instructions: Starting at the 'five stars' radio button, navigate to the 'Navigate backwards from here' link.

title: Navigate forwards to an unchecked radio button within a radio group
instructions: Starting at the 'one star' radio button, navigate to the 'two stars' radio button.

title: Navigate backwards to an unchecked radio button within a radio group
instructions: Starting at the 'two stars' radio button, navigate to the 'one star' radio button.

title: Navigate forwards to a checked radio button within a radio group
instructions: Starting at the 'one star' radio button, navigate to the 'two stars' radio button.

title: Navigate backwards to a checked radio button within a radio group
instructions: Starting at the 'two stars' radio button, navigate to the 'one star' radio button.

title: Check a radio button
instructions: Starting at the 'one star' radio button, check the radio button.

title: Check the next radio button in a radio group by navigating to it
instructions: Starting at the 'five stars' radio button, navigate to the 'one star' radio button.

title: Check the previous radio button in a radio group by navigating to it
instructions: Starting at the 'one star' radio button, navigate to the 'five stars' radio button.

title: Request information about an unchecked radio button
instructions: Starting at the 'one star' radio button, read information about the radio button.

title: Request information about a checked radio button
instructions: Starting at the 'one star' radio button, read information about the radio button.
